gsoap 生成 onvif 框架 #  生成参数 #  wsdl2h #  -O4 #  aggressively optimizes the output by &ldquo;schema slicing&rdquo; to remove unused schema components, see our article Schema Slicing Methods to Reduce Development Costs of WSDL-Based Web Services for details;
-P #  don&rsquo;t create polymorphic types inherited from xsd__anyType;
removes the base class xsd__anyType from the generated C++ classes, which are normally added by wsdl2h if the xsd:anyType XSD type is used somewhere in a WSDL.
